players.name: Brennan Davis
players.bio: Brendan Davis is collectively known as the Chicago Cubs best prospect. He is an athletic player that has great raw power and projects as a leadoff hitter

players.name: Brailyn Marquez
players.bio: Brailyn Marquez is a HARD throwing righty reaching 101 MPH with a great breaking ball. Has high ceiling.

players.name: Miguel Amaya
players.bio: Miguel Amaya is a catcher that is great behind the plate. He is a top 100 prospect, but we are waiting for the bat to show up.

players.name: Chase Strumpf
players.bio: Chase Strumpf was known as the best hitting 2B when he was drafted in 2019. He isn't known for his fielding, but he projects to stay at second.

players.name: Christian Hernandez
players.bio: Christian Hernandez is the best international player the Cubs have selected since Eloy Jiminez. He projects to be better.

players.name: Ed Howard
players.bio: Ed Howard is the Cubs 2020 first round draft pick.

players.name: Kohl Franklin
players.bio: Kohl has a high ceiling, but has lost two years of development due to Covid and Injury

players.name: Christopher Morel
players.bio: Chris Morel is a good hitter that can play multiple positions

players.name: Reggie Preciado
players.bio: The main prospect in the Yu Darvish trade.

players.name: Owen Cassie
players.bio: Redheaded power hitter in the ACL

players.name: Dakota Mekkes
players.bio: Righty with a unique arm slot that hides the ball

players.name: Jordan Wicks
players.bio: Lefty that will move fast with a great change piece
